{"tid":1470612,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"王丹：中共故技重施，故意挑釁示威者","createTime":"2019-08-14T06:01:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T07:26:41.000Z","uid":282677,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7ac8a1d4ad57d11dfc0f3457c305a6286eea83da","tid":1470612,"uid":282677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:01:35.000Z","msg":"大批市民昨晚於機場集結，導致多班航班取消，到晚上一名大陸人被懷疑大陸公安，以及一名《環球時報》記者，被包圍襲擊。八九學運領袖王丹今日Facebook 發帖回應事件，指中共「故技重施」，故意派人挑釁示威民眾，拍下被毆打的照片，並製造「香港人毆打中國人」的假新聞。他呼籲香港示威者面對故意挑釁的人，「把他們當空氣就好」。<br />\n<br />\n王丹憶述，1989 年六四前夕，中共曾把一輛破舊軍車丟棄於長安街上，然後把上車檢查的民眾誣指為「搶奪軍車，準備暴亂」，為六四開槍製造口實。看到昨晚香港機場有疑似公安的大陸人以及《環時》記者被圍，王丹認為中共現「故技重施」，派人用「苦肉計」，刻意挑釁示威民眾，繼而拍下被毆照片，在中國民眾中製造「香港人毆打中國人」的假新聞，同時為日後可能進行的鎮壓製造口實。<br />\n<br />\n經歷過八九民運的王丹又自稱「過來人」，指自己一看就知道中共想做什麼。他呼籲示威者：「對於故意挑釁的人，不理他們便是，讓他們自我表演，把他們當空氣就好。」<br />\n<br />\n他同時希望外界要明辨是非，相信示威者的理性，不會無緣無故暴力攻擊無辜者。他又指很多暴力衝突其實是中共派人假扮成示威者所為，他認為：「這方面，他們是慣犯」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%B7-%E7%92%B0%E6%99%82-%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E8%A2%AB%E5%9C%8D%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E7%8E%8B%E4%B8%B9-%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E6%95%85%E6%8A%80%E9%87%8D%E6%96%BD-%E6%95%85%E6%84%8F%E6%8C%91%E9%87%81%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85/?fbclid=IwAR0CqscpoHchEWYyvIaGGinEhJ9lanB63Q5RtQRL0KkPoRMXCIpS0hzN6uE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25B7-%25E7%2592%25B0%25E6%2599%2582-%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%259C%258D%25E9%2581%2587%25E8%25A5%25B2-%25E7%258E%258B%25E4%25B8%25B9-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E6%2595%2585%25E6%258A%2580%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%2596%25BD-%25E6%2595%2585%25E6%2584%258F%25E6%258C%2591%25E9%2587%2581%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0CqscpoHchEWYyvIaGGinEhJ9lanB63Q5RtQRL0KkPoRMXCIpS0hzN6uE&d=XnUAAdw%2Byae55KAVvns6w9LD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=0f163d38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25B7-%25E7%2592%25B0%25E6%2599%2582-%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%259C%258D%25E9%2581%2587%25E8%25A5%25B2-%25E7%258E%258B%25E4%25B8%25B9-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E6%2595%2585%25E6%258A%2580%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%2596%25BD-%25E6%2595%2585%25E6%2584%258F%25E6%258C%2591%25E9%2587%2581%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0CqscpoHchEWYyvIaGGinEhJ9lanB63Q5RtQRL0KkPoRMXCIpS0hzN6uE&h=c4b47e47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%B7-%E7%92%B0%E6%99%82-%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E8%A2%AB%E5%9C%8D%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E7%8E%8B%E4%B8%B9-%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E6%95%85%E6%8A%80%E9%87%8D%E6%96%BD-%E6%95%85%E6%84%8F%E6%8C%91%E9%87%81%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85/?fbclid=IwAR0CqscpoHchEWYyvIaGGinEhJ9lanB63Q5RtQRL0KkPoRMXCIpS0hzN6uE</a>"},{"pid":"4ea11c3391be937e678c843db060334987bec8d3","tid":1470612,"uid":18728,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:02:15.000Z","msg":"想轉移811視線<br />\n<br />\n唔好俾出面班分化引戰撚影響<br />\n818見"},{"pid":"8b8436376a6a3c2f72ed4d9348d1f6ae1ffd4d17","tid":1470612,"uid":56999,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PAtKQXt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPAtKQXt.jpg&h=77cd8239&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1RApQXu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1RApQXu.jpg&h=24b9aba0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7czFphu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7czFphu.jpg&h=2d5e6fd5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b94da3e796feee9f12fcd4e156fd402fd9fbb27","tid":1470612,"uid":282677,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:04:24.000Z","msg":"尋晚被綁果位完全係一臉勝利既咀臉<br />\n今日係大陸做埋英雄<br />\n大家真係要小心 冷靜行動"},{"pid":"d5166598ed3b612daabb6884fe9cb2c4ffc11cf5",